"NOWPayments allows you to accept credit card payments directly to your "
"crypto wallet. Funds go straight to your wallet – no middleman."
msgstr ""
"NOWPayments permet acceptar pagaments per targeta de crèdit directament al "
"teu moneder cripto. Els fons van directament al teu moneder – sense "
